Regex Tool, an interactive regular expression tester.
Copyright (c) 2010 Vincent Batoufflet <vincent@batoufflet.info>

Introduction
------------

Regex Tool is an interactive tool for testing Perl-style regular
expressions written in Python.

It uses Python GTK+ bindings for the GUI. The various .ui files has been
generated with the Glade interface builder.

Regex Tool is largely inspired by The Regex Coach which has been
developped by Edi Weitz and discontinued under it's Unices forms.

Features:

 * Interactive regular expression testing
 * Pattern match highlighting
 * Matching occurrences replacement and split

Changelog
---------

See ChangeLog file.

Installation
------------

Just run the following command:

   python setup.py install [--prefix=...]

